title: Is Popeye's Chicken Worth It?
itunes:title: Is Popeye's Chicken Worth It?
description:
Today on the show we opened up the phone lines to see what our listeners thought about the recent fatal stabbing of a man all because of the Popeye's Chicken sandwich, is it really worth it? Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to white supremacist Richard Spencer for his racist slurs and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee"
